hibernate-mapping.query: from TblEmployee t where (t.refRecordStatus.idstatus=1 or t.refRecordStatus.idstatus=3)
from TblEmployee t where t.refEmployeeType.idtype=:idType and(t.refRecordStatus.idstatus=1 or t.refRecordStatus.idstatus=3)
from TblEmployee t where t.codeFingerPrint=:code and(t.refRecordStatus.idstatus=1 or t.refRecordStatus.idstatus=3)
